    "These issues are compounded by the lack 1 arXiv:2401.15897v3 [cs.CY] 27 Aug 2024 of transparency and accountability surrounding the creation of these models [17,4,169].In answer to the mounting worry over the safety, security, and trustworthiness of generative AI models, practitioners and policymakers alike have pointed to red-teaming as an integral part of their strategies to identify and address related risks, with the goal of ensuring some notion of alignment with human and societal values [8,98,20].",
